{{Quote|Not long ago, I was hired as an instructor at an Authority university on Kalla. It is a place for higher education, mostly for Authority scions, a school rooted in technical education, commerce, and administration, with minimal stress on the humanities.|Rekkon|<ref name="HSSE" />}}
The '''University of Kalla''' on [[Kalla VII]] was a prestigious college in the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]] run by the [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Authority]]. It was a place of higher education for the children of influential Authority families, primarily. The institution was rooted in technical education, commerce, and administration, with minimal stress on the humanities. [[Rekkon]] was a teacher at the University.<ref name="HSSE" /> [[Hart-and-Parn Gorra-Fiolla|Fiolla]] of [[Lorrd/Legends|Lorrd]] was an exchange student at the university, studying political science.<ref name="HSCS">''[[Han Solo and the Corporate Sector Sourcebook]]''</ref>

